title: Trump-backed Jenkins 'feeling great' in W. Virginia race
text:
Trump-backed Jenkins 'feeling great' in W. Virginia race 3:14pm EDT - 01:18
U.S. Representative Evan Jenkins, one of the candidates that President Trump supported in a tweet Monday, said he was feeling ''great'' the day of the U.S. Senate primary race in West Virginia. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
